! 线性约束问题

$$
(f\mathbf A\bm b)\left\{\begin{aligned}
\min &\phantom{\{} f(\bm x)\\
\text{s.t.}&\left\{\begin{aligned}
\mathbf A\bm x&=\bm b\\
\bm x&\ge\bm 0
\end{aligned}\right.
\end{aligned}\right.
$$
